# ⏱ Stopwatch Pro

A modern, interactive stopwatch web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## 🚀 Features
- Start / Pause / Reset functionality
- Lap time tracking
- High precision timer (milliseconds)
- Responsive modern UI
- Smooth animations

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## 📌 Use Case
This project demonstrates DOM manipulation, event handling, and time-based logic — essential skills for frontend development.

